Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.05,0:01:23.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(1417,827)\c&H89F7F5&}Sao Cabal 三月19日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.98,0:01:33.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ha... chin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.62,0:01:42.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.45,0:01:44.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沉迷的彈珠游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.93,0:01:51.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“怎么看都是普通的石頭啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.03,0:01:54.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.01,0:02:01.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為這些石頭是普通石頭的想法 正是你的可悲之處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.14,0:02:05.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種石頭叫Forca Pedra(力量之石)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.19,0:02:09.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要帶在身邊就能趕走惡運的奇跡之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.95,0:02:12.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一般的石頭可是大不相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.47,0:02:17.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的指甲垢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.26,0:02:20.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎湯后服下能開啟你的神通力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.52,0:02:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 效果因人而異
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.59,0:02:25.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.01,0:02:27.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的使者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.92,0:02:29.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.03,0:02:32.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么... 意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有椅子吧 做我大腿上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.71,0:02:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.59,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 那副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.44,0:02:44.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像正在看著小偷一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.48,0:02:47.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.84,0:02:49.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.43,0:02:52.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的表情可不是什么天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.90,0:02:57.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 人的臉是顯示人體能量的計量器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:00.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上有很多惡氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么壞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.51,0:03:05.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是壞不壞的問題了 糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.43,0:03:06.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么辦啊 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.97,0:03:08.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的情況糟透了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.98,0:03:13.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 會怎樣啊 如果能夠看見未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:17.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能回避將要發生的災難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:19.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.81,0:03:20.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能辦得到嗎 大媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.30,0:03:24.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點貴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.77,0:03:30.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.26,0:03:32.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個城市里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.81,0:03:38.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.72,0:03:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！ 是不是指甲垢的功效啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.83,0:03:45.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.46,0:03:47.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是真家伙(指甲垢)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.99,0:03:49.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 Forca Pedra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.21,0:03:53.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.47,0:04:07.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.04,0:04:11.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我翻白眼可不是在演戲 是在通靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.46,0:04:15.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的靈魂離開了肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.13,0:04:21.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高飛起 現在我身處宇宙之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.95,0:04:24.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見時間之流 是通往未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.83,0:04:26.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你了 女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.64,0:04:27.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.53,0:04:29.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是“我”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.38,0:04:30.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在尋找著什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.68,0:04:31.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.73,0:04:33.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:34.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.19,0:04:35.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.62,0:04:37.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肖像畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.63,0:04:38.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肖像畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.98,0:04:42.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了 是你要找的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.58,0:04:43.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.84,0:04:48.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個孩子 建立了幸福的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.51,0:04:50.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么時候？在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.02,0:04:55.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久的將來 踏踏實實的努力會結出碩果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.19,0:04:56.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.80,0:05:00.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 注意你的右腳！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.44,0:05:04.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微小的不幸招致巨大的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.01,0:05:10.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧！ 不要去追逃走的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:12.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去！ 山！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.90,0:05:15.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要爬！ 槍聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.28,0:05:16.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.95,0:05:20.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的 會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.52,0:05:25.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.85,0:05:29.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大媽 Forca Pedra有效果嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:33.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效 非常有效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.55,0:05:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能救她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.61,0:05:35.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.60,0:05:38.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會得救嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.16,0:05:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.22,0:05:42.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.00,0:05:44.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指甲垢一起買了如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.26,0:05:47.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心套餐 特別優惠20%哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.76,0:05:51.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.91,0:05:57.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:05:58.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.66,0:06:01.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自便吧 我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:05.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗屎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.64,0:06:09.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是右腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.01,0:06:11.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 (占卜)是真家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.56,0:06:12.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了的話就過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:14.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.98,0:06:20.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hotel Venus : 維納斯旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.45,0:06:24.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 要出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.04,0:06:26.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.85,0:06:33.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫... 我回來之前你一步也不許出房門哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.50,0:06:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你的回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.58,0:06:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.32,0:07:10.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.97,0:07:14.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:20.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎... 么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 是Hiroshi哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.17,0:07:30.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi... 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.91,0:07:32.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.50,0:07:35.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個畫畫的 我請他幫了個忙 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.55,0:07:37.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.31,0:07:39.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.82,0:07:41.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上試試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.25,0:07:44.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.85,0:07:48.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么 是我的愛啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.46,0:07:52.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個 是鞋 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.88,0:07:54.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺在那里...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:55.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.68,0:07:56.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.04,0:07:59.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你為我買的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.08,0:08:01.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.22,0:08:02.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.30,0:08:04.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.72,0:08:08.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 別說的這么難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.30,0:08:09.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“請試穿一下吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.07,0:08:13.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是店員拿給我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.73,0:08:30.57,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(600,200)\pos(882,672)}三月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.97,0:08:38.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.59,0:08:58.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了 那個家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.64,0:09:06.15,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\pos(1392,706)\c&H221960&\bord0}新設計
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:16.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}招聘啟事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.25,0:09:19.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:21.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.96,0:09:24.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想工作 打工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.72,0:09:26.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里不需要小孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.28,0:09:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會拼命工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.66,0:09:30.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人開始都是這么說的 包括大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.93,0:09:33.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒人能堅持下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.20,0:09:34.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道為什么嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.73,0:09:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我Ram Yin非常能干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.37,0:09:38.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了的話 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.90,0:09:41.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.04,0:09:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也可能很能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.36,0:09:48.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試都沒試你憑什么斷定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.16,0:09:50.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.11,0:09:56.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.47,0:09:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Morenos...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.03,0:09:58.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.99,0:10:00.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Morehana？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.44,0:10:01.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.79,0:10:02.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看身份證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.96,0:10:03.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.79,0:10:05.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.55,0:10:09.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:12.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 為什么不穿鞋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.94,0:10:16.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還沒有付錢 工作賺錢后再去買
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.93,0:10:25.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.54,0:10:27.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我沒有去試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:30.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是小孩 工資減半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.43,0:10:32.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有身份證 再減一半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.61,0:10:34.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干的話 1天給你10Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.05,0:10:38.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要試用你 所以今天不給工錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.83,0:10:41.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身份可疑 所以明天也不給工錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:43.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后每天10Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.80,0:10:44.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.05,0:10:46.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.12,0:10:50.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 請不要叫我Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.30,0:10:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.61,0:10:54.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫Hana 我叫Ram
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.73,0:10:56.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.19,0:11:00.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人叫Hana的時候 會想起那些討厭的人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.78,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人就是羅嗦！ 那么叫你什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.56,0:11:07.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.38,0:11:08.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 Hachin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.67,0:11:09.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hachin？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.76,0:11:11.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜單要背下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.68,0:11:15.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后看到我這樣做 就是警戒的暗號 不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.03,0:11:16.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 警戒是什么意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.49,0:11:19.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五位客人光臨 要吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.30,0:11:36.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 認識這家伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.88,0:11:38.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:42.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.04,0:11:44.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔能再看一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.41,0:11:47.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是在看我的胸脯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.94,0:11:49.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.91,0:11:52.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么這張怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:54.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.74,0:12:03.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.65,0:12:12.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.24,0:12:19.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事！ 根本不像是父女嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.96,0:12:31.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓人替你擔心啊 這個家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.78,0:12:32.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.73,0:12:41.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎餃三份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.69,0:12:44.82,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(500,0)\pos(446,1006)\c&HB4FFFF&}超級飯店 三月21日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.63,0:13:02.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.09,0:13:10.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.55,0:13:14.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級飯店 別想吃霸王餐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.80,0:13:16.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉我記住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.25,0:13:18.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓老子用功夫送你下地獄！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.18,0:13:28.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有個Hatchin這么大的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過更能干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.41,0:13:34.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 從沒失敗過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.65,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.62,0:13:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你和沒你都一樣 沒用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.48,0:13:44.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我很溫柔 還會試用你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.61,0:13:46.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天還是沒有工錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.00,0:13:49.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么哼哼哈哈的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.06,0:13:51.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.79,0:13:54.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不溫柔！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.10,0:14:17.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鼓起干勁了 會像變了個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.07,0:14:27.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這個家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.65,0:14:30.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在什么地方見過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.92,0:14:32.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？ 在哪里見過？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.25,0:14:33.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.97,0:14:37.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想一想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.00,0:14:41.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊貧民區外圍的一間房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.47,0:14:43.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.71,0:14:47.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.28,0:15:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.11,0:15:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.19,0:15:21.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個家伙 再跟過來 就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.58,0:15:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦！ 付錢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.21,0:15:30.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的... 鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.66,0:15:45.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.20,0:15:50.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要爬山！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.00,0:16:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.05,0:16:25.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.07,0:16:35.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.24,0:16:42.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的！ 會死的！ 會死！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.56,0:16:53.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.68,0:16:55.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.44,0:17:18.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡之石？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.95,0:17:29.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.76,0:17:53.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼！ 要我放火燒了你的鳥窩頭嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.42,0:17:56.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 明明是你沖過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.64,0:18:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 是Hatchin嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.69,0:18:04.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊？ 穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.17,0:18:06.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王餐...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.75,0:18:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.43,0:18:08.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.58,0:18:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.55,0:18:11.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事 閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.01,0:18:12.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大媽？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.85,0:18:16.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見嗎 大媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.85,0:18:18.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我在你的大咪咪上開個洞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.12,0:18:23.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你在和誰說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.46,0:18:24.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么！ 你這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.42,0:18:26.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.47,0:18:28.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不見！ 你剛才在說什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.61,0:18:29.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.02,0:18:30.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么大媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.20,0:18:40.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.40,0:18:47.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大... 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.32,0:18:51.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.91,0:18:53.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 給我記住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.45,0:18:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.16,0:19:01.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.13,0:19:04.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.57,0:19:35.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.51,0:19:39.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老公！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.13,0:19:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.80,0:19:53.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.89,0:19:55.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.90,0:19:58.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Hiroshi吧 是爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:03.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？ 很像啊 非常像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.81,0:20:07.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 不是的 不是Hiroshi啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.99,0:20:14.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.65,0:20:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.10,0:20:22.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:26.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來那張肖像畫真的像他本人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.97,0:20:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像不像都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.41,0:20:31.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個帥哥的事實又不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.28,0:20:35.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 都是那個占卜的老太婆不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.39,0:20:37.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有預測中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.33,0:20:39.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么踏實的努力啊 傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.22,0:20:44.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測中了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.48,0:20:45.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.48,0:20:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是沒死嗎 活蹦亂跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.52,0:20:49.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個死老太婆 下地獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.05,0:20:51.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次讓我再遇見 要好好揍她一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.47,0:20:52.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許攔著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.10,0:20:58.39,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 除了肖像畫之外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.75,0:21:00.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得占卜都預測中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.55,0:21:05.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果真的能在這里見到父親的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.36,0:21:09.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會是怎樣的表情啊
